  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5542432/" class="title-link">威尔·金里卡的《多元文化公民权》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5542432"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/wangxuanzhi/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u49410195-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/wangxuanzhi/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">璇玑座</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-08-11"
      class="main-meta">2012-08-11 23:33:45</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5542432_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                          这本书应该算是我这学期看到的对我论文理论架构最有价值的一本书了，作为一个英美系的作者，金里卡写的书逻辑脉络很清晰，观点也明确，对比于德沃金和罗尔斯那些人的书，算是出乎我的意料了。从全文结构来看，他的第五章和第六章才是“硬货”，通过此部分我终于找到了 ...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5542432/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5542432_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5542432_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
